CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1946, pg. 25 reads: "Summer Housewarming - Mr. and Mrs. Freeland Shaw of Kelly Street recently entertained with an elaborate housewarming. Guests included Mr. and Mrs. Chauncey Adams, The Rev. and Mrs. W.L. Shaw, Mr. and Mrs. B.F. Watkins, Mrs. Susie Huddlerton, Mrs. Sophia Douglas, Mrs. Beulah M. Shoppard, Mrs. Fannie Garreth and Mrs. Leona Dickerson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Freeland Shaw and Mrs. Shaw seated at head of table, with guests including Chauncey Adams, Mrs. Adams, Rev. W. L. Shaw, Mrs. Shaw, B. F. Watkins, Mrs. Watkins, Susie Huddlerton, Sophia Douglas, Beulah M. Shoppard, Fannie Garreth, and Leona Dickerson, in dining room of Shaw home, Kelly Street
